sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Server
    participant D as Database

    U->>B: Open SPA URL<br/>https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
    B->>S: GET /spa
    S-->>B: HTML page
    Note right of B: Browser loads HTML shell

    B->>S: GET /main.css and GET /main.js
    S-->>B: CSS and JavaScript files
    Note right of B: Browser executes JS<br/>and builds dynamic UI

    B->>S: GET /data.json
    S-->>B: JSON list of notes
    Note right of B: Browser renders notes dynamically on page

    U-->>B: Interacts with page without full reload